<br>
I usually have my stuff up for sale for much more than I sold it, hoping someone will buy it.  I sold the Frosty this morning for 7500, leaving me about 10k to purchase a new weapon or something.<br>
<br>
Is the Frostbringer the best weapon I can get for 10k?<br>
<br>
Obviously I need something that brings aggro.  I have reviewed the &quot;aggro&quot; list in this forum, but Frosty seems to be the best thing for the money on this list.<br>
<br>
Here are other things I see for sale.  Please let me know if one of them is better for the money or should I just buy another Frosty.<br>
<br>
Wrapped Entropy Serpant Spines - 8k<br>
Wavecrasher - 8k<br>
Spiked Velium Mallet - 8k<br>
Widebladed Greatsword - 8k (should I buy this as a nice 2hander and just wait to build up money for another 1hander?)<br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
<br>
