<br>
I have never used most of the others except the spiked velium mallet which I found to be underwelming aggro but my dex was low (no avatar yet) so it seemed to never proc.<br>
<br>
One weapon I am going to keep my eye out for though is a 2hb from BOT.  It was 31/30 and proc'd Planar Stun.  I had a very hard time getting aggro from a 62 warrior using it in PoD and just let him tank.  I think it was Great Staff of Thunder but cannot remember the name.<br>
